Work in small sections at a time, starting at a corner edge and working methodically across the tray. Paint a small area of the tray's corner with glue, then add a dab of glue to each pebble. {"smallUrl":"https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/9/9c/Make-a-Pebble-Boot-Tray-Step-3Bullet1.jpg/v4-459px-Make-a-Pebble-Boot-Tray-Step-3Bullet1.jpg","bigUrl":"https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/9/9c/Make-a-Pebble-Boot-Tray-Step-3Bullet1.jpg/v4-759px-Make-a-Pebble-Boot-Tray-Step-3Bullet1.jpg","smallWidth":460,"smallHeight":306,"bigWidth":760,"bigHeight":506.31868131868134,"licensing":"<div class="mw-parser-output"><p>License: <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/3.0/">Creative Commons</a><br>
</p><p><br />
</p></div>"}

Press the pebble in place. Keep the pebble as flat as possible––the surface should not be too bumpy for the boots and shoes to sit on. {"smallUrl":"https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/5/51/Make-a-Pebble-Boot-Tray-Step-3Bullet2.jpg/v4-459px-Make-a-Pebble-Boot-Tray-Step-3Bullet2.jpg","bigUrl":"https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/5/51/Make-a-Pebble-Boot-Tray-Step-3Bullet2.jpg/v4-759px-Make-a-Pebble-Boot-Tray-Step-3Bullet2.jpg","smallWidth":460,"smallHeight":306,"bigWidth":760,"bigHeight":506.31868131868134,"licensing":"<div class="mw-parser-output"><p>License: <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/3.0/">Creative Commons</a><br>
</p><p><br />
</p></div>"}

Repeat for each pebble in that section. {"smallUrl":"https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/4/46/Make-a-Pebble-Boot-Tray-Step-3Bullet3.jpg/v4-459px-Make-a-Pebble-Boot-Tray-Step-3Bullet3.jpg","bigUrl":"https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/4/46/Make-a-Pebble-Boot-Tray-Step-3Bullet3.jpg/v4-759px-Make-a-Pebble-Boot-Tray-Step-3Bullet3.jpg","smallWidth":460,"smallHeight":306,"bigWidth":760,"bigHeight":506.31868131868134,"licensing":"<div class="mw-parser-output"><p>License: <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/3.0/">Creative Commons</a><br>
</p><p><br />
</p></div>"}

Move onto the next section. Move across and add pebbles according to your pattern or randomly. {"smallUrl":"https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/7/72/Make-a-Pebble-Boot-Tray-Step-3Bullet4.jpg/v4-459px-Make-a-Pebble-Boot-Tray-Step-3Bullet4.jpg","bigUrl":"https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/7/72/Make-a-Pebble-Boot-Tray-Step-3Bullet4.jpg/v4-759px-Make-a-Pebble-Boot-Tray-Step-3Bullet4.jpg","smallWidth":460,"smallHeight":306,"bigWidth":760,"bigHeight":506.31868131868134,"licensing":"<div class="mw-parser-output"><p>License: <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/3.0/">Creative Commons</a><br>
</p><p><br />
</p></div>"}
